title: Alex.Jones.Show.2009.01.13-chakra71
description:
The Alex Jones Show

Tuesday January 13, 2009.

Jason Bermas sits in for Alex. On today's show, Jason talks with Larry Pratt, executive director of Gun Owners of America, Jonas Stoltzfus of the Pennsylvania Independent Consumers and Farmers Association, and Maurice Thompson of the Buckeye Institute about the paramilitary style execution of a search warrant against the Manna Storehouse in Ohio. Jason also talks with Marty Schachter of the Cal Ben Soap Company. 

Hour-1: News and open lines
Hour-2: Ted Anderson then Marty Schachter and open lines
Hour-3: Larry Pratt then open lines
Hour-4: Jonas Stoltzfus then Maurice Thompson
